      <h1>The Real Estate Investor Mindset: How Successful Investors Think About Property</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Real estate creates more millionaires than almost any other asset class — but most people approach it emotionally. Learn the mental models that separate successful real estate investors.</p>
